{"tid":1977480,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"共產黨最叻人民鬥人民 比卡超咩鬥黃呀而家","createTime":"2020-04-18T04:18:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-18T11:03:44.000Z","uid":124604,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8ec0effa2e7992e6db5d8d2425745492c5ae1fe9","tid":1977480,"uid":124604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T04:18:12.000Z","msg":"慎防建制文革式人民鬥人民文宣毒招<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%92%AD%E6%AF%92/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2592%25AD%25E6%25AF%2592%2F&d=0xR7vGHOl893LUq1yoppelcETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=9d36a083\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2592%25AD%25E6%25AF%2592%2F&h=6603094c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%92%AD%E6%AF%92/</a> <br />\n<br />\n你老母成班弱智仔都冇發現 而家共產黨啊方向都轉曬<br />\n上年呀幾撚多五毛<br />\n而家一條毛都搵唔到啦<br />\n全部人民鬥人民! 黃鬥黃<br />\n<br />\n好撚心你哋班旁觀者咪撚柯南上身<br />\n有人聲稱&quot;爆料&quot;<br />\n屌你哋班旁觀者有一窩蜂衝去討論 玩狼人殺咩而家<br />\n又唔係第一身喺度帶晒風向<br />\n<br />\n唔係叫你哋盲目支持<br />\n真心唔撚知就唔好中二病柯南上身9UP 幾下<br />\n風向就係咁帶出嚟<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>結論: <br />\n自己唔係第一身唔知道事情嘅真相 唔好亂出聲 <br />\n如果幫手帶錯曬啲風向 <br />\n狼人勝利遊戲結束</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"7d46a8563abe426af2144f29f393165f1ad46b78","tid":1977480,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T04:20:48.000Z","msg":"支那最鐘意拉一派打一派"},{"pid":"3bb4c41593c8f9193bfec465cf40ab637202ae74","tid":1977480,"uid":124604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T04:28:21.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"a876ca805ac880072dc8b9f2c08fa7c879f354b8","tid":1977480,"uid":124604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T10:58:54.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"8b037fb3494670094891a1674404321e7be52f7b","tid":1977480,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2